cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper deals with incorporating visual information into text representation, which suggests that it could belong to multiple sub-categories. 

- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category as the paper deals with text embeddings and improving text understanding. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also likely as the paper incorporates visual information into text representation. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible sub-category as the paper proposes a new architecture that outperforms previous approaches. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible sub-category as the paper deals with improving text understanding, which is relevant to information retrieval tasks. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible sub-category as the paper deals with multimodal approaches that incorporate both text and visual information.
